====== H8068: שָׁמִיר ======

===== Source =====

from  H8104  in the original sense of  ;

===== Meaning =====

pricking a  thorn ; also (from its  keenness  for scratching) a gem, probably the  diamond

===== Definitions =====

  - pricking
  - thorn
  - keenness
  - diamond

===== Usage =====

adamant (stone), brier, diamond.
